        "content": "<p>bacek opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12803\">PR #12803</a> from <code>bacek:wasm-c-api-tag</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Upstream wasm-c-api was updated to include <code>Tag</code>. This is migration from wasmtime specific to the upstream.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Move tag type info into wasm.h alongside other core types instead of a separate wasmtime/tag.h header</li>\n<li>Remove wasmtime/tag.h (contents merged into wasm.h / wasm.hh)</li>\n<li>Update extern.hh and tag.hh to reflect new layout</li>\n<li>Add tag param accessors in <a href=\"http://func.rs\">func.rs</a></li>\n<li>Refactor <a href=\"http://tag.rs\">tag.rs</a> to match updated C API surface</li>\n<li>Update <a href=\"http://tag_type.cc\">tag_type.cc</a> tests accordingly</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>",
